{
  "texts": [
    "We base our implementation on (Karachev and Xu, 2025) with modifications to adhere more closely to the original ControlNet design.",
    "We train the models on a four 80 GB A100 GPU cluster for 5000 training steps, which takes approximately one day.",
    "Training uses an instantaneous batch size per device of 1, with two gradient accumulation steps, for an effective batch size of 8.",
    "Full hyperparameter details are listed in Appendix A.1.",
    "We propose a benchmark dataset for both force prompting models using images that we curate from Pexels."
  ]
}